To connect Follow Up Boss with the Luxury Presence platform, follow these steps:

Generate an API Key in Follow Up Boss:

• Log in to your Follow Up Boss account.
• Navigate to Admin > API.
• Click Create API Key, name it (e.g., "Luxury Presence"), and copy the key 

Then, connect the API Key in Luxury Presence:

• Log in to the Luxury Presence dashboard.
• Go to Settings > CRM Integrations.
• Click Add New, select Follow Up Boss as the provider, and paste the API key.
• Save the integration. 

